Class XFastTrieWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • algorithms.bipartite.XFastTrieWrapper
  • public class XFastTrieWrapper
extends java.lang.Object
    a wrapper for the XFastTrie to provide methods of a minimum heap that can handle more than one node of the same key.

    nichole
